&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MDgxMzM2OQ==&amp;amp;mid=2649747247&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=15eec2801a3a0d562a5b3198a888b3e4&amp;amp;chksm=881ea9f9bf6920ef9cfd5af4f8291656a3f204ce6086317c9076091c8750094142293c726f92&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-itemshowtype=&quot;0&quot; data-linktype=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;祁寯藻给曾国藩使绊子的猜想：恨天对其弟不公&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
